---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Privacy Policy | Schedule.Makeup',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 mx-auto lg:px-8 lg:py-20 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="font-bold font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-tighter tracking-tighter mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-4xl dark:prose-invert">
      <p>At Schedule.Makeup, we respect the privacy of makeup artists and their clients. This policy outlines how we handle data.</p>
      
      <h3>Data Collection</h3>
      <p>We collect studio information (name, vanity URL preference, and service links) to facilitate the setup of your booking engine. We do not sell artist or client data to third-party advertisers.</p>

      <h3>Google Business Integration</h3>
      <p>When we assist with Google Business Profile integration, we do not require your password. We guide you through the process using public links to ensure your studio's security remains 100% intact.</p>

      <h3>Payment Security</h3>
      <p>All payments are processed securely via PayPal or Stripe. Schedule.Makeup does not store credit card information on our servers.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
